fr.xebia.management.jms

Class ManagedConnectionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.xebia.management.jms.ManagedConnectionFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManagedConnectionFactoryMBean, javax.jms.ConnectionFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SpringManagedConnectionFactory

    public class ManagedConnectionFactory
extends Object
implements javax.jms.ConnectionFactory, ManagedConnectionFactoryMBean

    JMX MBean compatible wrapper of a ConnectionFactory.

    Expose MBean attributes and methods via a standard xxxMBean interface rather than with spring annotations to support usage without Spring

    Author:
    Cyrille Le Clerc

      • dumpAllOpenedResources

        public List<String> dumpAllOpenedResources()
        Description copied from interface: ManagedConnectionFactoryMBean

        List of opened connection / session / message producer / message consumer / topic subscriber.

        Only available if trace-leaks is enabled. Otherwise, an empty list is returned.
